{
    "comment_thread": {}, 
    "video_length": "PT10M5S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "Hi!", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Can everybody hear me?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I want to talk about\na couple things today.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Three, actually.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Summer camp, the Internet", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and making tough choices.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Over the summer,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I spent every waking hour", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "watching over\n25 spectacular fifteen-year-olds,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "whether that&#39;s hearing\nabout their latest crush", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or staying up late at night\ntalking about God.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Being a camp counselor has taught me\nsome really important things.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One of my campers, his name is Jonah,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he&#39;s actually right next to me up there,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is brilliant.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Might be the smartest person\nI&#39;ve ever met in my entire life.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He understands the nuance\nof complex concepts", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "better than I ever could", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and every time I talk to him\nI learn something new.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Jonah also has a twin brother\nwhose name is Micah,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "who&#39;s impeccably well-dressed,\na social butterfly", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and attracts friends and attention\nwherever he goes.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Growing up in parallel to that\nhas been really difficult for Jonah.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, a couple months back\nwe were at a camper union", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and Jonah wasn&#39;t acting like himself.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He was frustrated and aggressive.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I was upset\nthat he wasn&#39;t feeling comfortable.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I pulled him aside\nand we got to chatting.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And after couple of minutes\nhe turns to me and says:", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Oz,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "does happiness exist?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve been wondering for some time now", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I&#39;m having a hard time thinking", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that it&#39;s not just some illusion we make up", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to feel better about\nthe brokenness of the world around us.&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it took me a minute", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to respond because I felt\nso ashamed and embarrassed.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not because I hadn&#39;t done anything\nto make his life better", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but because I wasn&#39;t sure\nthat I disagreed with him.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I took a moment,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "thought to myself:", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;When I was his age,\nwhat would I have said?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What would I have done?&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When I was 15,\nI got a chance to meet a different boy.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "His name was Elijah\nand he was 6 years old.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "At the age of 6,\nhe was diagnosed with PDD-NOS", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which is a condition\non the autism spectrum", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that affected his interpersonal\ncommunication and social skills.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Every Sunday we&#39;d meet up for two hours\nat the local synagogue", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to play basketball,\ndo some arts and crafts,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "maybe even get to talking\nabout Thomas the Tank Engine", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or how annoying his little brother is.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After a while,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "either because he became more confident\nor comfortable around me", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or because the situation escalated,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he started telling me about his family.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How his parents would sometimes\nget into violent arguments,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or that his father would beat him.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And hearing that I felt terrified and sad", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because I knew I had two choices.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One of which was to say something", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "knowing that he&#39;d be pulled\nout of the program", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and might have more pain caused to him,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or I would live with the guilt\nof having said nothing.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So when his mom came\nto pick him up that day,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I told her what he&#39;d said,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and after that\nI never saw Elijah ever again.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I felt so guilty because I knew", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that what I&#39;d done\nput him further in harm&#39;s way.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I knew I&#39;d done the right thing\nbut it didn&#39;t feel good,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it didn&#39;t feel glamorous.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I felt still unsettled.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Just to change gears for the time being,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "today technology has transformed\nthe way we do good", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in some pretty spectacular ways.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;ve seen nations toppled by Twitter,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "beautiful moments of solidarity\non Facebook", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and one video\ndrawing the world&#39;s attention", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to a terrible war crime in Africa.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Controversy or not.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Inspired by these moments,\nmy roommate and I,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "his name is Ben Erinsson,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I think he&#39;s in the audience\nsomewhere,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "decided we would switch things up", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with our fraternity&#39;s philanthropy,\ncalled Derby Days.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We reached out\nto our networks and the Internet,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the people that we were connected to", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and asked them to believe\nin the power of one another.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We worked day in and day out for our goal", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of raising $50,000 for cancer research,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with sleepless nights, telling ourselves", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that on the other end we&#39;d feel gratified,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like we made a difference\nand changed something in the world,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that there would be\nthis innate feeling of accomplishment.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We started a hashtag,\nbuilt a social media presence", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that engaged 30,000 people,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "planned events that had real meaning\nand substance to them,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we filmed videos of sorority women", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sharing the stories\nof how cancer had affected their lives,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "some of which had never shared\nthose stories with their friends before,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in ways that were\nso powerful and meaningful", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that they brought people to tears.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And after a few weeks", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we broke a new GW record", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and raised over $80,000\nfor cancer research.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The next morning I woke up\nexpecting to feel accomplished", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and instead I felt empty", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and sad.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was in a dark place.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Instead of seeing the things\nthat were right in front of my eyes,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this beautiful, fantastic thing\nthat we just put together,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I could only hear people complain\nthat their sorority didn&#39;t win,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or that their apparel order\ndidn&#39;t go through.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The age that we live in", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "has put us all in a dark place.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Somewhere or another with this expectation", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that the world&#39;s going to be glamorous", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we sometimes fall short of that.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was in that dark place after Derby Days,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when I was at the camper union with Jonah,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "talking about whether or not\nhappiness exists.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I could only answer with something\nI realized in that moment,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I turned to him and said: &quot;Dude!", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We create happiness\nfor ourselves in our lives.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Sure,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s invented.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yeah sure,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s different for everyone.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yeah sure,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sometimes people pretend to be happier\nthan they actually are,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that&#39;s OK,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because it&#39;s on us to decide", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "who we&#39;re going to be.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And what makes us happy.&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The Internet", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "has made doing good feel a lot easier", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and more glamorous,\nand more gratifying than it actually is.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve spent the last 5 years of my life\nfeeling guilty", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I sent a 6-year-old\nin a harm&#39;s way,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "trying to do the right thing.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And at one point I kind of realized", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there&#39;s nothing else I could have done.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s kind of how life is sometimes.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One of my favourite quotes,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "goes something like this:", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Each of us must hold a note\nin both of our pockets,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "one that says:", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;For my sake were the heavens\nand the earth created&quot;.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the other which says:", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;I am but dust and ashes.&quot;&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s our duty to spend our lives\nendevouring every day", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to make the world a better place,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to struggle endlessly in this quest", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to fix this ever broken wonder\nof a universe.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s not just about\nwhat we do and how we feel,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "those moments in which\nwe&#39;re there for each other", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in even the smallest ways,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you and I both know\nhave the greatest impact.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s not just about feeling good\nabout what we&#39;re doing,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s about realizing\nthat the picture is bigger than us.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Do people whine less because\nwe raised $80 grand for cancer research?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because gratification comes from in here.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not from anybody else.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Doing good is harder\nthan the YouTube videos make it seem", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because it&#39;s not about you.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Selflessness is hard.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s uncomfortable.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s challenging.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Everybody doing a little thing\nis not enough to see big change.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A million tweets won&#39;t feed\nthe hungry or cure the sick.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A YouTube video alone", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "won&#39;t put a kid from an underserved\ncommunity through college.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But you know what?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I bet your hard work might.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Jonah and Elijah taught me", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that happiness is not always\nwhat we think that it is.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That doing the right thing\ndoesn&#39;t always merit you a parade.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That true happiness comes from\nselflessness and vulnerability,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not chasing something shiny\nto fulfill you.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We do good,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because it&#39;s the right thing to do.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;re selfless because\nit&#39;s the right thing to do,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not because we need\na reminder of our virtue,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because chances are\nthat if you do good, you are good.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s good enough.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I dare you to be brave.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The stumbling blocks on our path\nto changing the world,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "exist only in our minds.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We might not feed the world overnight,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but that doesn&#39;t excuse us from trying", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because we need big dreamers", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
